/*Query: For each employee, display the first_name, personality, the name of any projects theyÂ´ve chosen and the number of incompatible workers according with the table bellow:
-----------------------------------------------------------------
Personality Type | ... is incompatible with
-----------------------------------------------------------------
INFP             | ISFP, ESFP, ISTP, ESTP, ISFJ, ESFJ,ISTJ, ESTJ
_________________________________________________________________
ENFP             | ISFP, ESFP, ISTP, ESTP, ISFJ, ESFJ, ISTJ, ESTJ
_________________________________________________________________
INFJ             | ISFP, ESFP, ISTP, ESTP, ISFJ, ESFJ, ISTJ, ESTJ
_________________________________________________________________
